sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as Llama Stack Operator<br/>redhat-ods-applications
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process)
    participant LLSDPod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant IngressCtrl as Ingress Controller<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (informer cache)<br/>ServiceAccount Token auth
    Operator->>Operator: Read feature flags ConfigMap<br/>(enableNetworkPolicy, imageMapping)
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from base templates
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: Apply transformers:<br/>FieldMutator, NamePrefix,<br/>Namespace, NetworkPolicy
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service (ClusterIP 8321)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ServiceAccount<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update PVC (if storage configured)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update NetworkPolicy (if enabled)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update PDB, HPA, RoleBinding<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Ingress (if exposeRoute=true)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,LLSDPod: CA Bundle Aggregation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read odh-trusted-ca-bundle ConfigMap<br/>(auto-detected)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read user CA bundle ConfigMaps<br/>(from spec.server.tlsConfig.caBundle)
    Operator->>Operator: Validate PEM certs (X.509)<br/>Max 10MB, 1000 certs
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed CA ConfigMap<br/>{instance}-ca-bundle

    Note over Operator,LLSDPod: Status Probing
    Operator->>LLSDPod: GET /v1/health<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLSDPod-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LLSDPod: GET /v1/providers<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLSDPod-->>Operator: Provider health info
    Operator->>LLSDPod: GET /v1/version<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLSDPod-->>Operator: Server version
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update LlamaStackDistribution/status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,LLSDPod: Flow 2: External Client Access (exposeRoute=true)
    Client->>IngressCtrl: HTTP request<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    IngressCtrl->>LLSDPod: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLSDPod-->>IngressCtrl: Inference response
    IngressCtrl-->>Client: HTTP response

    Note over Client,LLSDPod: Flow 3: Internal Client Access (default)
    Client->>LLSDPod: {instance}-service.{ns}.svc.cluster.local<br/>8321/TCP HTTP<br/>NetworkPolicy enforced
    LLSDPod-->>Client: Inference response
